Download the rst file generator from below location
https://github.com/varspool/sphpdox

Run the sphdox command with proper arguments

./vendor/bin/sphpdox process --output="/home/dhanushka/Work/bitcasa/CloudFS-PHP/docs/sphinx/source/sdk"

When prompted enter the below
Namespace of code to document:  no-namespace
Path to namespace:  /home/dhanushka/Work/bitcasa/CloudFS-PHP/cloudfs

Goto the sphinx folder
cd docs/sphinx

Generate the sphinx documentation with below command
make html